{"tid":2036023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共斥日方提病毒源自中國是過河拆橋 違中日合作抗疫方針","createTime":"2020-05-26T08:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:05:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3edbd07d80add68c9a310a8cb0543ab1e912bea1","tid":2036023,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:27:15.000Z","msg":"外交部反駁安倍言論 指有違中日共同抗疫努力<br />\n26.05.2020 15:58<br />\n<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三指，新型冠狀病毒從中國擴散到世界是事實，北京提出反駁；外交部發言人趙立堅說，中方堅決反對將病毒來源問題政治化、污名化，這種做法有悖於世界衛生組織及大量研究機構、醫學專家的專業意見，更有違國際社會包括中日兩國共同抗擊疫情的努力和期待。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅強調，病毒源頭是嚴肅的科學問題，必須以事實和科學為依據，由科學家和醫學專家去研究，政治盲從不應凌駕於科學判斷，團結合作才是人類戰勝疫情的最有力武器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290672&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1290672%26csid%3D261_367&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=b8232e2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1290672&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"fc2696bd32f0e08a02f6ecafaafda9b87e9b8014","tid":2036023,"uid":47356,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"點解中國仲可以咁厚顏無恥同人講武術肺炎唔係你地研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9790b0f28fa15ff9e8de86ac683ca2fe922ca7b","tid":2036023,"uid":286103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fc2696bd32f0e08a02f6ecafaafda9b87e9b8014","tid":2036023,"uid":47356,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"點解中國仲可以咁厚顏無恥同人講武術肺炎唔係你地研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"支那一向都無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da9fc9f1e3154feb98cafc9d24a5fed5737bdbb","tid":2036023,"uid":145928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08: